data.description: Seller motivated and helps with closing costs. !!! Don't miss out on this beautiful property, WELCOME HOME, HEATED POOL, to this charming 3 bed, 2 bath home with 2 car garage and huge living room. This house is a must see!! Upon entering the home you are greeted by a wonderful spacious floor plan that opens to the large dining room and family room. NEW vinyl fence,  all with pavers around the property, You can sit back and relax while enjoying the serenity of the green space. NEW ROOF 2016. NEW HVAC 2018. NEW irrigation 07/2021, NEW paint inside, UPDATED kitchen with granite countertops, NEW microwave 2022, many unique touches throughout including a . The master suite is an oasis of comfort, NEW and updated master bath with a beautiful jacuzzi for relax, NEW fixtures inside and out. a NEW vanity in the master bathroom and much more. Water connected to the city (NOT WELL) Additional storage space. Close to several GREAT schools!  Other rooms in the home are spacious and flexible, ready to adapt to your changing lifestyle. Modern light fixtures and accents add a contemporary touch to the already well-designed interior. The neutral shades of paint envelop the entire home, providing a versatile canvas for your personal decor. Outdoor living is a delight, with a fenced backyard offering both security and a sense of seclusion. Enjoy the Florida sunshine on your screened-in patio, a perfect spot for relaxing or entertaining. This Spring Hill gem is more than just a house; it's a lifestyle. With no HOA or CDD fees, you have the freedom to enjoy your property to the fullest. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience this remarkable home for yourself!  BEAUTIFUL READY TO WELCOME A FAMILY. Call us today to schedule an appointment!
